  P/BV & Price per Share / Book value per share \\
  \hline
\end{tabular}
\hfill \\
\hfill \\


\hfill \\
\begin{tabular}{l p{4cm} p{4cm}}
    & \textbf{Numerator} & \textbf{Denominator} \\
